{"tid":1530324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續做外過文宣，大家入黎。","createTime":"2019-09-02T02:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T02:31:10.000Z","uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"07da7ff28a70b6989e84da02f81a32e60e2429f8","tid":1530324,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"今明兩日罷工罷學，大家都有小小時間抖下，休息同時都做下文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>A) 繼續鼓吹美國立人權法。</strong><br />\n而立法重點:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 請美國國會通過人權法案<br />\nPlease pass Hong Kong Human Right and Democracy Act. <br />\n<br />\n2. 制裁香港、支那官員<br />\nImpose sanction on officials of HK and China in violation of human right.<br />\n<br />\n3. 給予香港自治，否則請制裁香港。<br />\nGrant a true autonomy(i.e. dual universal sufferage) for HK( under the USA's monitoring), or impose sanctions on HK by cancelling United States&ndash;Hong Kong Policy Act.</strong></span><br />\n(第三點請附上呢張圖)<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/US7qSOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUS7qSOm.jpg&h=05ad5cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOewOeN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOewOeN.jpg&h=86b582eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiTJEmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiTJEmt.jpg&h=939ccd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7T9zUP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7T9zUP.jpg&h=88207342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mE35SGu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmE35SGu.jpg&h=f8d1a6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBgCJOa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBgCJOa.png&h=1cac44fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GKVLSGw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/